{"tid":873711,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"吳亦凡選秀節目驚見學員唱EXO作品　f(x)宋茜在旁食花生","createTime":"2018-10-23T15:31:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-27T09:42:17.000Z","uid":193951,"like":7,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"b7efcfa9b2c73c3715890fe3437a13030d2ca76f","tid":873711,"uid":193951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T15:31:05.000Z","msg":"吳亦凡在2012年以韓國組合EXO成員身份出道，不過在2014年向當時所屬公司提出解約，並回到中國內地以演員和歌手身份發展。雖然吳亦凡在接受傳媒訪問時，沒有迴避有關EXO的提問，不過吳亦凡近日為東方衛視選秀節目《下一站傳奇》嘉賓時，有選手在吳亦凡面前表演EXO的《Overdose》，令吳亦凡難掩尷尬神色。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CoZcd5M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCoZcd5M.jpg&h=50addd66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n吳亦凡在2012年以EXO成員身份出道，並於2014年向SM娛樂提出解約。<br />\n<br />\n《下一站傳奇》由吳亦凡、韓國組合f(x)中國成員宋茜、周筆暢、陳偉霆、鄧紫棋，以及羽泉樂隊的胡海泉擔任導師。昨晚（22日）播出的第一集中，選手劉阡羽竟在吳亦凡等人面前表演EXO的《Overdose》，<span style=\"color: red;\">特別是這首歌是吳亦凡向SM娛樂提出解約前最後一首參與的主打歌，所以吳亦凡一開始感到愕然，其後流露尷尬的神情</span>，而現時仍屬SM娛樂的宋茜在導師席上亦笑着在旁觀察。不過，吳亦凡等相當欣賞劉阡羽的實力，最後劉阡羽全票過關，可見吳亦凡未有因為對方獻唱EXO作品而留難對方。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JK9zsp2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJK9zsp2.jpg&h=234c1816&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n選手劉阡羽表演EXO《上癮》時，吳亦凡神色尷尬。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f7efWit.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff7efWit.jpg&h=d029e9f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n至今仍屬SM娛樂的宋茜則觀察身旁的吳亦凡。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8RjWFLs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8RjWFLs.jpg&h=beda3129&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n同屬導師的G.E.M非常享受劉阡羽的表演。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CLJcYxc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCLJcYxc.jpg&h=0c2d8a1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n幸好吳亦凡仍非常欣賞劉阡羽實力，投票讓她過關。"},{"pid":"5f0add8fa33961ea8b82ba5c72e63e5ba75c5a42","tid":873711,"uid":74065,"like":1,"dislike":13,"score":-12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T15:32:41.000Z","msg":"凡凡真係好公正<br />\n<br />\nBTW V媽個樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d4d9616b0daef27c45d7bb4dab7c0935216a05a","tid":873711,"uid":193951,"like":2,"dislike":27,"score":-25,"quote":{"pid":"5f0add8fa33961ea8b82ba5c72e63e5ba75c5a42","tid":873711,"uid":74065,"like":1,"dislike":13,"score":-12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T15:32:41.000Z","msg":"凡凡真係好公正<br />\n<br />\nBTW V媽個樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T15:34:18.000Z","msg":"凡凡真係好型好skr🤙<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cUYMizd.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcUYMizd.gif&h=78a5e7c5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a8cd8bc26b49020fdbb39c6c454ee546ac16959f","tid":873711,"uid":80814,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T15:41:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/23/233806_ef7d711905c81038b49f4585a4d7fa21.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F23%2F233806_ef7d711905c81038b49f4585a4d7fa21.jpg&h=fd26ed0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「乜Kris係rapper咩？我剩係記得佢喺EXO嗰陣首Overdose咋，嗰陣嘅Kris最值得欣賞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」"},{"pid":"ef4831c063b072216aedd791256642f7be5a6c0c","tid":873711,"uid":52073,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T15:42:03.000Z","msg":"凡哥就係牛b"},{"pid":"45edeb30fa1a0f54a21d95fb313d641e511c1549","tid":873711,"uid":162377,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T15:55:58.000Z","msg":"應該尷尬嘅位係 個女仔唱跳都好過煩煩多多聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32be2e7ac2680e64b0af7723be4436b45a6d81d4","tid":873711,"uid":80814,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T01:27:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/24/092655_6d8b8f16c33a23c297cb4b01c9388c27.png\" data-thu